<body>

  <div id="background"></div>

  <div id="main">

    <div id="intro">
      <h1>SpotaTweet</h1>
      <p>Pump up the volume! A Spotify &amp; Twitter API mashup.<br />Tweet will update every 10 seconds and play
        the<br />latest Spotify track posted to Twitter.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="tweet-holder"></div>

  </div>

  <span class="github">Source available on <a href="https://github.com/twitterdev/spotatweet"
      target="_blank">Github</a>.</span>

  <script src="javascripts/SpotaTweet.js"></script>

  <script>
